Suggests: libqt2.2-dev, qt2.2-doc, kdbg, kdelibs3-dev, kdebase, kdelibs3-doc, htdig, sgmltools, gettext, a2ps, enscript, gv, qt-designer | kde-designer, glimpse, ark, kpaint, kbabel, kiconedit, gdb
Description: An IDE for Unix/X11
 KDevelop is an easy to use Integrated Development Environment
 for developing C/C++ applications under X11. It features 
 project management, an advanced editor, a class browser
 and an integrated debugger.
 .
 The application wizard can generate fully functional frameworks
 for terminal programs and programs based on Qt, KDE or GNOME.
